These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, nurse
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, australian
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, subway
1. the nurse is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
2. the photographer is on the right of the nurse##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | milk      | cola    |
| Job           | nurse | photographer |
| Nationality   | canadian       | australian  |
| Transport     | roller      | subway     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, apricot
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, electronic
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
2. the person eating apricot is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | apricot | eggplant |
| Music-Genre   | house       | electronic         |
| Pet           | frog     | guinea-pig         |
| Transport     | quad-bike    | skateboard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, entrepreneur
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, metal
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, trike
1. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the writer##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | drawing          | cooking |
| Job           | entrepreneur | writer     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz            | metal         |
| Transport     | trike         | bike   |

 #################################

 
