.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, cabbage
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, funk
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, jet-ski
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of techno is the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | coffee |
| Food          | cabbage   | pumpkin |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | techno     |
| Transport     | subway | jet-ski     |

 